data.description: Hurry and make your appointment to see this super cute home. This two bed one bath ranch home is move in ready to call your own. The living room and bedrooms have hardwood floors. All the appliances are included. The back yard is very large for the area and is fenced in. Close to downtown,shopping,GVSU and John Ball Zoo.  Attention investors, this property is certified with the city of Grand Rapids. At the request of the owners any and all offers will be due on Tuesday, February 20 at .noon
